overview: On August 14th live on FITE is the second part of GCW's Homecoming 2022. The first four matches are already announced and you can check them below:  Rina Yamashita vs Sawyer Wreck  Mike Bailey vs Joe Lando  Charli Evans vs Cole Radrick  Dark Sheik vs Maki Itoh
title: GCW Homecoming 2022, Part 2
